NewSpring Mezzanine




NewSpring Mezzanine partners with business owners and financial sponsors to support growth, acquisitions and recapitalizations by providing flexible capital solutions with mezzanine debt and equity.
As former CEOs, operating executives and as experienced investors, the NewSpring Mezzanine team brings a complete business view to the strategic capital needs of the companies where we invest. We temper our insights with reflection on various economic cycles and inform our decisions with an internal partnership built on diverse backgrounds. We believe this different, time-tested way of thinking, of considering the comprehensive needs of the business we are entrusted to support, has been the core principle of our success.
From this experience, we understand that no two companies are the same. NewSpring Mezzanine tailors financial solutions to a business owner's immediate needs as well as long-term strategic goals, and we have the temperament to ensure preparation holds steadfast where the best of plans may not always survive intact. In this way, we offer a business owner the most flexible approach to finance different situations and changing goals. With this customized approach, NewSpring delivers a complete capital structure including debt, equity and our trusted partnerships with senior lenders and equity partners.











