Investment Criteria




NewSpring Mezzanine maintains a disciplined investment strategy that provides business owners and financial sponsors with flexible capital solutions including mezzanine debt and equity to support growth, acquisitions and recapitalizations.


Transaction Types:



Sponsored and non-sponsored transactions including acquisitions, shareholder liquidity, recapitalizations, growth capital and refinancings 
NewSpring Mezzanine has the ability to consider control transactions independently or while also working with other financial sponsors 

Industries:



Industry agnostic with significant experience in technology, healthcare, business and consumer services and niche manufacturing 

Company Financial Profile:



At least $20mm in revenue and $2mm in EBITDA
Sustainable margins and cash flows  



Geography:



East of Chicago for non-sponsored companies
Across the U.S. for financial sponsored companies 
















